==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Torsional
<hw>Tor"sion*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining
to torsion; resulting from torsion, or the force with which a thread or
wire returns to a state of rest after having been twisted round its
axis; <as>as, <ex>torsional</ex> force</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Torsion electrometer</ent>⟦br⟧
